          "reviewBody": "My son is an ex pointer of this school.. this school has given my son a very good environment to study, friend circle and good teachers .. it is one of the best schools in Kolkata never matter ..\nAlthough there is a catch here. There are cases of bullies and ragging in this school Often students face mental problems like depression and anxiety because this institution gives a lot of pressure on students through academics . The admission test of class 11 for the science stream is conducted in pcm subject and believe me it is the next jee advanced paper after IIT. Sphs sets that level of question for admission of internal students in class 11.\nDon't be afraid . If you are planning your son / daughter to study in this school then I would recommend it . I can promise that this school will groom your child perfectly in science, maths and English that his/her basics in the subjects will be very strong .",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
