            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "South Point High School, located in Kolkata, is one of the largest and most reputed educational institutions in the city. Known for its academic excellence, rich cultural heritage, and holistic development programs, South Point High School stands as a beacon of quality education. Here's an overview:\n\n1. Academic Excellence:\nSouth Point High School is affiliated with the West Bengal Board of Secondary Education (WBBSE) and WBCHSE for secondary and higher secondary education. It maintains high academic standards, preparing students for board examinations and competitive entrance tests.\n\n2. Holistic Development:\nThe school emphasizes holistic development, offering a well-rounded education that includes academics, sports, arts, and extracurricular activities. It focuses on nurturing students' overall growth and personality development.\n\n3. Infrastructure:\nSouth Point High School boasts modern infrastructure with spacious classrooms, science and computer laboratories, libraries, auditoriums, and sports facilities to support comprehensive learning and development.\n\n4. Faculty:\nThe school has a team of experienced and dedicated teachers who are committed to providing quality education. They use innovative teaching methods to engage students and foster a passion for learning.\n\n5. Cultural Heritage:\nSouth Point High School has a rich cultural heritage with a legacy spanning decades. It organizes various cultural events, festivals, and celebrations, promoting cultural diversity and harmony among students.\n\n6. Extracurricular Activities:\nThe school offers a wide range of extracurricular activities including sports, music, dance, drama, debates, and clubs. Students have ample opportunities to explore their interests and talents beyond academics.\n\n7. Community Engagement:\nSouth Point High School encourages parental involvement and organizes various events, seminars, and workshops where parents actively participate. It fosters a strong sense of community and collaboration.\n\n8. Leadership Opportunities:\nThe school provides leadership opportunities through student council, clubs, and various events, allowing students to develop leadership skills and teamwork.\n\n9. Alumni Network:\nSouth Point High School has a strong alumni network comprising successful professionals in various fields. The alumni provide support, guidance, and mentorship to current students.\n\n10. Achievements and Recognition:\nThe school has received numerous accolades and recognition for academic achievements, sports accomplishments, and contributions to society, maintaining its reputation as a leading educational institution.\n\nSouth Point High School continues to uphold its legacy of excellence in education, shaping the lives of students and preparing them to excel in all spheres of life with knowledge, skills, and values.",
